### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Certificate Validation
To verify that auto-enrollment and CA propagation were working, the following commands were run:

```bash
gpupdate /force
certutil -pulse
certutil -user -pulse

These commands:
	‚Ä¢	Forced Group Policy refresh
	‚Ä¢	Triggered certificate auto-enrollment
	‚Ä¢	Requested user- and machine-level certificates

üì∏ Certificate Enrollment & Command Verification


